content: I think the MoSCoW Method and the PDSA framework are really helpful. I'll try to use those to prioritize my tasks better. I also realize that I need to focus on one task at a time to make progress. I've been trying to do too many things at once and it's not working out. By the way, I usually spend about 15 minutes having a quick breakfast every morning, so I need to make sure I'm using my time efficiently.
